title: @OspreyWGolf Tees Off Monday in Pinehurst Challenge
text: @OspreyWGolf Tees Off Monday in Pinehurst Challenge North Florida Athletics LIVE SCORING PINEHURST, N.C. -- The North Florida women's golf team continues it's fall tournament schedule at the Pinehurst Challenge with 36 holes of play set to begin Monday morning on Course No. 1 (par 72 / 5,949 yards) at historic Pinehurst Country Club.The Ospreys look to build on their solid third-place finish at the JU Classic on Sept. 28-29. The Pinehurst Challenge is a two-day, 54-hole competition that features a field of 20 teams with UNF the lone representative from the Atlantic Sun Conference.North Florida sends a veteran lineup to the competition highlighted by a quartet of seniors along with an experienced junior.
